  §§§ Unordered lists ⦉
  ¶ ⦊
    ‖ Unordered lists are denoted by \⁝. ⦉
  ⦉

  ¶ ⦊
    ‖ Example 1 ⦉
    <code>
      ⁝ ⦊
        ‣ apples ⦉

        ‣ oranges ⦉

